bodylog.logic

Class Session

  • java.lang.Object
    • bodylog.logic.abstracts.VariableList
      • bodylog.logic.Session

  • public class Session
extends VariableList
    The second component in the logical hierarchy. Contains a date and a list of Sets. The date is written to and read from session files.
    See Also:
    Move, Set

      • maxSetSize

        public int maxSetSize()
        Checks the size of each Set contained in this Session and returns the largest value. When writing Sets to file each will be the same size but when reading from file they may be of different length. Not used in anything yet.
        Returns:
        the length of the largest Set
